title: Humboldt Reports Filing Its Interim Report for the Six Months Ended June 30, 2015
text:
August 26, 2015 17:48 ET Humboldt Reports Filing Its Interim Report for the Six Months Ended June 30, 2015 
CALGARY, ALBERTA--(Marketwired - Aug. 26, 2015) - Humboldt Capital Corporation (TSX VENTURE:HMB) announces that it has filed the Management's Discussion and Analysis and Financial Statements for the six months ended June 30, 2015 on SEDAR and the company's website.
